    </p>
    <figure align="">
        <image source="WriteMethods/Figures/we2-code-highlight.png" alt="Write a private method"/>
    </figure>
    <program language="java">
        <input>
public void cheerful (String a, String b, String c) {}
        </input>
    </program>
    <p>A call to this method would look like: <c>obj.cheerful("alpha", "beta", "gamma");</c>
    </p>
